        <mxCell id="1429" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=3;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 72px;&quot;&gt;Contributing to the project:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 60px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;1. Update the EM in the first commit of you slice branch. Name the branch to reflect the Command or the State View you are working on.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;2. Make PR for the change into main branch so that others can see that you&#39;re working on that slice&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;3. Implement the slice&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 28px;&quot;&gt;4. Make PR for the new version of the branch to complete the slice work into main.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
